{"title":"烽火台（图片）","authors":["李有祥　郭辉"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":4,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"烽火台"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李有祥摄　郭辉诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要问：这里曾点燃过烽烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月的流云已剥蚀了骨骸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要说：这里曾发生过拚杀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史的尘沙已将忠魂掩埋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就是历史，任时代更迭变幻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——明和暗、光和亮、静和动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就是碑刻，向苍穹无声诉说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——荣与辱、生与死、血与火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为根除战争，我愿消溶于寂静，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为忘却屈辱，我独自走向荒漠。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}